Package io.sentry

Class ExperimentalOptions

java.lang.Object
io.sentry.ExperimentalOptions
public final class ExperimentalOptions extends Object
Experimental options for new features, these options are going to be promoted to SentryOptions before GA.

Beware that experimental options can change at any time.
